title: Dean Martin - Italian Love Songs 320k remastered musicfromrizzo

Dean Martin - Italian Love Songs (orig 1962 LP) (remastered 2015) 320k (musicfromrizzo)

Here's Mr. Dean Martin with some greatest songs of course, including one of
my most favourite of the genre. "I have but one heart"  ('O Marenariello)
from Mario Puzo's Godfather movie series starring Mr. Al Pacino and
beautiful Diane Keaton, in which it was sung originally by the great
Mr. Al Martino (we have lots of his best music posted here for you too)

Please seed this great music to the family and all interested - grazie

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
